      <body><div type="address"><address><addrLine><pb facs=""/>Herrn D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi> Arthur Schnitzler</addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#68" type="place">Wien XVIII</rs></addrLine><addrLine><rs ref="#133" type="place">Spöttelgasse 7</rs></addrLine></address></div><div type="writingSession" n="1"><opener><dateline rend="right"><pb facs="MS-B-00005-B-000-00190"/><date>7. 1. 04</date></dateline><salute>Lieber Arthur!</salute></opener><p>Kannſt Du mir die Adreſſe des D<hi rend="superscript">r</hi><space unit="chars" quantity="1"/><rs ref="#2199" type="person">Stefan Epſtein</rs> in <rs ref="#182" type="place">Paris</rs> ſchreiben? Bitte ſei ſo lieb.</p><p>Mir gehts recht ſchlecht.</p><closer>Deine <rs type="person" ref="#2173" subtype="implied">Frau</rs> beſtens grüßend bin ich<lb/>herzlichſt<lb/>Dein alter<lb/><signed>HermannBahr</signed></closer></div></body>
